                <expan>Rob<ex>er</ex>t</expan> Thorne <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr>
                <expan>and</expan></choice>to Nicholas Thorne <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr>
                <expan>and</expan></choice> oon John Goodriche clerke or to the
                <expan>on<ex>e</ex></expan> ?lyvers of them <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr>
