                <expan>w<ex>ith</ex>in</expan></choice> one yere next after the date 
                hereof <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>and</expan></choice> in the seid house
                <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>and</expan></choice> hospitall of Seint
